    "description": "學生經由基礎繪畫的訓練,培養對形體敏銳的觀察力和扎實的表現能力，並結合藝術美學，充分運用在創作與設計。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 造形語言與掌握技巧<br>2. 線條與輪廓<br>3. 空間的透視概念<br>4. 光線、明暗、陰影和體積關係<br>5. 空間和質量<br>6. 質感和筆觸的表現-1<br>7. 質感和筆觸的表現-2<br>8. 靜物描繪 1<br>9. 靜物描繪 2<br>10. 設計美學的構圖觀念<br>11. 形的聯想<br>12. 綜合媒材創作<br>",
        "en": "1. Shape Language with Master Skill. <br>2. Line and Outline. <br>3. The Concept of Spatial Perspective. <br>4. Lighting and Shading Skills for Volume Creation. <br>5. Space for Mass. <br>6. Texture with Brushwork. <br>7. Texture with Brushwork. <br>8. Still Life Drawing I. <br>9. Still Life Drawing II. <br>10. Composition for Design Aesthetics. <br>11. To associate with Shape in Thinking. <br>12. Mixed-Media Creation."
